summaries.short: Get the inside story on the 'Vice Principals' series premiere with super dope notes from co-creator Danny McBride.
summaries.full: A funny--and irreverent--take on cast commentary, "Dope Doodles" gives you the inside story on the series premiere of dark comedy 'Vice Principals.' This half-hour episode is filled with notes straight from the mind of co-creator and star Danny McBride, and loaded with fun facts from director Jody Hill, star Walton Goggins, and many more.
